ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng H\u00e1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 40 - 43 (sau C\u00f4ng nguy\u00ean), gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i n\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, t\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c. Ng\u00e0y nay, \u0111\u1ec1n Hai B\u00e0 Tr\u01b0ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m tham quan du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi du kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi mi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1735794124.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1735789485822.jpg","total_access":"45"},{"id":"224","lat":"20.949897491993305","lon":"106.14839138415337","district_id":"15","code":"13fe9d84310e77f13a6d184dbf1232f3","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m B\u00e1c H\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 th\u0103m B\u00e1t Tr\u00e0ng","title_en":"Place where Bac Ho visited Bat Trang","description":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m B\u00e1c H\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 th\u0103m l\u00e0ng B\u00e1t Tr\u00e0ng, x\u00e3 B\u00e1t Tr\u00e0ng, huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed quan tr\u1ecdng, g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19 th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m 1958, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 th\u0103m l\u00e0ng B\u00e1t Tr\u00e0ng, m\u1ed9t l\u00e0ng ngh\u1ec1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 g\u1ed1m s\u1ee9, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n, th\u0103m h\u1ecfi nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1734054325.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1735871850667.jpg","total_access":"80"},{"id":"281","lat":"21.14959459996509","lon":"105.88886103945853","district_id":"14","code":"e3796ae838835da0b6f6ea37bcf8bcb7","author":"IAHK","title":"\u0110\u00ecnh L\u1ed7 Kh\u00ea","title_en":"Location where Ho Chi Minh visited Lo Khe village","description":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m, L\u1ed7 Kh\u00ea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t x\u00e3 c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec7n \u0110\u00f4ng Ng\u00e0n, ph\u1ee7 T\u1eeb S\u01a1n, tr\u1ea5n Kinh B\u1eafc. T\u1eeb n\u0103m 1961 \u0111\u1ebfn nay L\u1ed7 Kh\u00ea thu\u1ed9c x\u00e3 Li\u00ean H\u00e0, huy\u1ec7n \u0110\u00f4ng Anh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1734079774.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1734664038714.jpg","total_access":"75"},{"id":"215","lat":"20.903505869946898","lon":"105.58231070279466","district_id":"24","code":"3b8a614226a953a8cd9526fca6fe9ba5","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"Cao \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ed3i D\u1ecbnh (TT Xu\u00e2n Mai)","title_en":" Dinh hill peak (Xuan Mai town)","description":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n C\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng th\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Cao \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110\u1ed3i D\u1ecbnh, Th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Xu\u00e2n Mai, huy\u1ec7n Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ef9, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n C\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng Th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u0103m 1945. Cao \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110\u1ed3i D\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec7n Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng M\u1ef9 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea5u tranh gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp t\u1ef1 do cho d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1735295172.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1735294039708.jpg","total_access":"53"},{"id":"220","lat":"21.058655602422807","lon":"105.98682671427119","district_id":"15","code":"ec8ce6abb3e952a85b8551ba726a1227","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"Di t\u00edch c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn Trung M\u1ea7u","title_en":" Trung Mau revolutionary relics","description":"Trung M\u1ea7u thu\u1ed9c huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, ngo\u1ea1i Th\u00e0nh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e1ng 8\/1945 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a hai l\u00e0ng Trung M\u1ea7u v\u00e0 Th\u1ecbnh Li\u00ean, t\u1ed5ng D\u0169ng Vi, huy\u1ec7n Ti\u00ean Du, t\u1ec9nh B\u1eafc Ninh. C\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u0103m 1945 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, n\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ed9ng ho\u00e0 ra \u0111\u1eddi, do c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1p nh\u1eadp li\u00ean x\u00e3, hai l\u00e0ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean l\u00e0 x\u00e3 Trung H\u01b0ng. ","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736410484.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736393433251.jpg","total_access":"45"},{"id":"283","lat":"21.029930074514663","lon":"105.97103015608171","district_id":"15","code":"0f49c89d1e7298bb9930789c8ed59d48","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"\u0110\u00ecnh H\u00e0n L\u1ea1c (Gia L\u00e2m)","title_en":"Han Lac Communal House (Gia Lam)","description":"\u0110\u00ecnh H\u00e0n L\u1ea1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u0103n h\u00f3a quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ed5 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1edd c\u00e1c v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n, anh h\u00f9ng d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi l\u00e0ng x\u00e3.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736410107.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736406498471.jpg","total_access":"39"},{"id":"214","lat":"21.018359444274484","lon":"105.97266385780806","district_id":"15","code":"ca46c1b9512a7a8315fa3c5a946e8265","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u00e2n T\u1ea3o (Gia L\u00e2m)","title_en":"Tran Tao communal house (Gia Lam)","description":"\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u00e2n T\u1ea3o c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng T\u00e1o thu\u1ed9c x\u00e3 Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecb, huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.","image":"..\/viewer\/panoramas\/preview\/pano_1736407346193.jpg","panorama_image":"pano_1736407346193.jpg","total_access":"41"},{"id":"236","lat":"20.947222237638886","lon":"105.89661272908893","district_id":"15","code":"01161aaa0b6d1345dd8fe4e481144d84","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi nh\u1edb t\u1ed9i \u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c M\u1ef9 t\u1ea1i th\u00f4n Trung Quan (V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c)","title_en":"The place to remmber the crimes of American imperialism in Trung Quan village (V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c commnue)","description":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi nh\u1edb t\u1ed9i \u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c M\u1ef9 t\u1ea1i th\u00f4n Trung Quan (V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed quan tr\u1ecdng, ghi d\u1ea5u nh\u1eefng t\u1ed9i \u00e1c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tranh ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1965-1972, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e9m bom d\u1eef d\u1ed9i nh\u1eb1m ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ebft h\u1ea1i d\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng.","image":"..\/viewer\/panoramas\/preview\/pano_1736407933159.jpg","panorama_image":"pano_1736407933159.jpg","total_access":"44"},{"id":"228","lat":"21.08111147370337","lon":"105.90492146325275","district_id":"15","code":"74db120f0a8e5646ef5a30154e9f6deb","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"Nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y g\u1ea1ch H\u01b0ng K\u00fd (TT Y\u00ean Vi\u00ean)","title_en":"Hung Ky brick factory (Yen Vien district)","description":"Nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y g\u1ea1ch H\u01b0ng K\u00fd (Th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Y\u00ean Vi\u00ean, Gia L\u00e2m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong ng\u00e0nh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t g\u1ea1ch ng\u00f3i, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng trong khu v\u1ef1c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng l\u00e2n c\u1eadn.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736411986.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736397315016.jpg","total_access":"45"},{"id":"230","lat":"21.023489539159495","lon":"105.99327149433509","district_id":"15","code":"6da9003b743b65f4c0ccd295cc484e57","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0ng Giao T\u1ea5t (Kim S\u01a1n)","title_en":"Giao Tat village battle (Kim Son)","description":"Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0ng Giao T\u1ea5t (Kim S\u01a1n) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p, di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i l\u00e0ng Giao T\u1ea5t (Kim S\u01a1n), huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n ta m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u0169 trang v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736412165.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736398366423.jpg","total_access":"43"},{"id":"234","lat":"21.005736666667","lon":"105.96991833333","district_id":"15","code":"289dff07669d7a23de0ef88d2f7129e7","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00e0 c\u1ee5 H\u01b0\u01a1ng Giai (D\u01b0\u01a1ng X\u00e1)","title_en":"Location of Mr. Huong Giai's house (Duong Xa)","description":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00e0 c\u1ee5 H\u01b0\u01a1ng Giai (D\u01b0\u01a1ng X\u00e1) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed quan tr\u1ecdng g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p, t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i th\u00f4n D\u01b0\u01a1ng X\u00e1, x\u00e3 D\u01b0\u01a1ng X\u00e1, huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ghi d\u1ea5u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u1ee5 H\u01b0\u01a1ng Giai v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tranh gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736409972.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736405503499.jpg","total_access":"49"},{"id":"226","lat":"21.023856325419146","lon":"105.97608118707613","district_id":"15","code":"9cfdf10e8fc047a44b08ed031e1f0ed1","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecba Ph\u00fa Th\u1ee5y (Gia L\u00e2m)","title_en":"Phu Thuy Battlefield (Gia Lam)","description":"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecba Ph\u00fa Th\u1ee5y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecba ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n M\u1ef9 t\u1eeb h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Trong c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1966, 1967, 1968, 1969 v\u00e0 1972, t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecba n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eafn r\u01a1i 14 m\u00e1y bay c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n M\u1ef9. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 12-1972, Ti\u1ec3u \u0111o\u00e0n 93 Trung \u0111o\u00e0n 261 \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u0169 trang v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n huy\u1ec7n Gia L\u00e2m, chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u anh d\u0169ng, xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, b\u1eafn r\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 3 \"ph\u00e1o \u0111\u00e0i bay\" B.52, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u201cH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i - \u0110i\u1ec7n Bi\u00ean Ph\u1ee7 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng\u201d.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736411026.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736395245296.jpg","total_access":"39"},{"id":"200","lat":"21.307994779320033","lon":"105.84836787419303","district_id":"13","code":"3644a684f98ea8fe223c713b77189a77","author":"IAHK","title":"Di t\u00edch c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng T\u00e2n Y\u00ean","title_en":"Tan Yen revolutionary relic","description":"Di t\u00edch c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng T\u00e2n Y\u00ean: Bia l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m chi b\u1ed9 T\u00e2n Y\u00ean ghi d\u1ea5u vi\u1ec7c th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp chi b\u1ed9 \u0110\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec7n \u0110a Ph\u00fac (huy\u1ec7n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n ng\u00e0y nay), hi\u1ec7n nay thu\u1ed9c khu h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh s\u1ed1 6, th\u00f4n T\u00e2n Y\u00ean, x\u00e3 H\u1ed3ng K\u1ef3, huy\u1ec7n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736497194.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736495844686.jpg","total_access":"56"},{"id":"208","lat":"21.248923333333","lon":"105.73336","district_id":"13","code":"091d584fced301b442654dd8c23b3fc9","author":"IAHK","title":"T\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i th\u00f4n Ninh Ki\u1ec1u","title_en":"Ninh Kieu village monument","description":"\u0110\u00e0i t\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec7m c\u00e1c n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n b\u1ecb m\u00e1y bay B52 c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 n\u00e9m bom gi\u1ebft h\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam 28\/12\/1972.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736502573.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736495986388.jpg","total_access":"45"},{"id":"209","lat":"21.271464481953444","lon":"105.78593428557133","district_id":"13","code":"b1d10e7bafa4421218a51b1e1f1b0ba2","author":"IAHK","title":"C\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00ecnh Ph\u00fa","title_en":"Phu communal house revolutionary base (Phu Thinh) (Minh Phu)","description":"Minh Ph\u00fa c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea5u tranh ch\u1ed1ng gi\u1eb7c ngo\u1ea1i x\u00e2m t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm. \u0110\u1ea7u th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 XX, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn l\u1edbn thanh ni\u00ean trong v\u00f9ng Kim Anh - \u0110a Ph\u00fac theo ngh\u0129a qu\u00e2n \u0110\u1ec1 Th\u00e1m, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng Cai T\u00f4n (ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4n Thanh Tr\u00ed) c\u0169ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y tham gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng ngh\u0129a qu\u00e2n \u0110\u1ec1 Th\u00e1m","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736505057.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736496058062.jpg","total_access":"62"},{"id":"221","lat":"21.21041186347135","lon":"105.84916042522784","district_id":"13","code":"060ad92489947d410d897474079c1477","author":"IAHK","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u00e1y bay B52 b\u1ecb b\u1eafn r\u01a1i t\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng Chu\u00f4m","title_en":"Memorial site for the incident where the B52 plane was shot down at Chuom field (Phu Lo)","description":"QPT\u0110- 20 gi\u1edd 13 ph\u00fat ng\u00e0y 18-12-1972, chi\u1ebfc m\u00e1y bay B-52 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00fang t\u00ean l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a ta b\u1ed1c ch\u00e1y v\u00e0 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng Chu\u00f4m thu\u1ed9c x\u00e3 Ph\u00f9 L\u1ed7, huy\u1ec7n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc B-52 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb k\u00edp chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ec3u \u0111o\u00e0n 59, Trung \u0111o\u00e0n T\u00ean l\u1eeda 261 (\u0110o\u00e0n Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ngay trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736734261.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736732724679.jpg","total_access":"47"},{"id":"250","lat":"21.299971709601888","lon":"105.86215228047041","district_id":"13","code":"6c9882bbac1c7093bd25041881277658","author":"IAHK","title":"Di t\u00edch c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn Trung Gi\u00e3","title_en":"Relics of the Trung Gia resistance war","description":"Di t\u00edch c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 Trung Gi\u00e3, hi\u1ec7n nay thu\u1ed9c th\u00f4n Xu\u00e2n S\u01a1n, x\u00e3 Trung Gi\u00e3, huy\u1ec7n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1733905192.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736500427111.jpg","total_access":"66"},{"id":"249","lat":"21.201848333333","lon":"105.78362","district_id":"13","code":"077e29b11be80ab57e1a2ecabb7da330","author":"IAHK","title":"S\u1edf ch\u1ec9 huy d\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn trung \u0111o\u00e0n 921","title_en":"Field Command of Regiment 921 (Phu Cuong)","description":"Q\u0110ND - S\u1edf ch\u1ec9 huy d\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn Trung \u0111o\u00e0n 921 (S\u01b0 \u0111o\u00e0n 371) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1ea1i l\u00e0ng Th\u1ee5y H\u01b0\u01a1ng, x\u00e3 Ph\u00fa C\u01b0\u1eddng, huy\u1ec7n Kim Anh, t\u1ec9nh V\u0129nh Ph\u00fac (nay l\u00e0 huy\u1ec7n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n, TP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i). T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, trung \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 huy nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1ebb vang c\u1ee7a Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9, c\u1ee9u n\u01b0\u1edbc.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1733903411.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736501895768.jpg","total_access":"79"},{"id":"248","lat":"21.25728024689848","lon":"105.86282819560684","district_id":"13","code":"621bf66ddb7c962aa0d22ac97d69b793","author":"IAHK","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i N\u00fai \u0110\u00f4i","title_en":"Memorial site of the revolutionary resistance event at Nui Doi (Soc Son)","description":"N\u00fai \u0110\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba danh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong cu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c M\u1ef9. \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 hai ng\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhau, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng tr\u00f9 ph\u00fa. N\u00fai \u0110\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00ec c\u1ea3nh quan thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u00ec vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tranh.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736824987.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736732339142.jpg","total_access":"48"},{"id":"219","lat":"21.23640321987961","lon":"105.90410256294128","district_id":"13","code":"c0e190d8267e36708f955d7ab048990d","author":"IAHK","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u00e1y bay B52 b\u1ecb b\u1eafn r\u01a1i t\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng Tr\u1ea7m","title_en":"Memorial site for the downed B52 plane in Tram field (Xuan Giang)","description":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u00e1y bay B-52 b\u1ecb b\u1eafn r\u01a1i t\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng Tr\u1ea7m, x\u00e3 Xu\u00e2n Giang, huy\u1ec7n S\u00f3c S\u01a1n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t di t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed quan tr\u1ecdng trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tranh ch\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i - \u0110i\u1ec7n Bi\u00ean Ph\u1ee7 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng\" (12\/1972). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00ean l\u1eeda SAM, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eafn r\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1y bay B-52 c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n M\u1ef9 trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c oanh t\u1ea1c h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t nh\u1eb1m v\u00e0o H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736732590.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736505083639.jpg","total_access":"62"},{"id":"227","lat":"21.19707478582424","lon":"105.62267988643116","district_id":"17","code":"705f2172834666788607efbfca35afb3","author":"hieu(vr360)","title":"Bia Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Mai Kh\u00ea - V\u1ea1n Y\u00ean","title_en":"Mai Khe Victory Stele","description":"Bia Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Mai Kh\u00ea - V\u1ea1n Y\u00ean","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1736751943.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1736738479123.jpg","total_access":"100"},{"id":"51","lat":"21.059437115377484","lon":"105.7877910985649","district_id":"5","code":"2838023a778dfaecdc212708f721b788","author":"Admin","title":"Ch\u00f9a Th\u00e1nh Ch\u00faa","title_en":"Thanh Chua Pagoda","description":"","image":"..\/viewer\/panoramas\/preview\/pano_1701746189893.jpg","panorama_image":"pano_1701746189893.jpg","total_access":"50"},{"id":"58","lat":"21.02873056223547","lon":"105.79903349980754","district_id":"5","code":"66f041e16a60928b05a7e228a89c3799","author":"Admin","title":"Ch\u00f9a B\u00e1o \u00c2n","title_en":"Bao An Pagoda","description":"","image":"..\/viewer\/panoramas\/preview\/pano_1701748938799.jpg","panorama_image":"pano_1701748938799.jpg","total_access":"27"},{"id":"54","lat":"21.044950032601125","lon":"105.80419634331935","district_id":"5","code":"a684eceee76fc522773286a895bc8436","author":"Admin","title":"\u0110\u00ecnh An Ph\u