Son).","description":"","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753427967.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753427292837.jpg","total_access":"17"},{"id":"350","lat":"21.151155378365928","lon":"105.50816727490046","district_id":"30","code":"9de6d14fff9806d4bcd1ef555be766cd","author":"linhttd","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m LNSK Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch HCM, Trung \u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u1ea3ng, Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdp, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00ecnh Ph\u00f9 Xa (Vi\u00ean S\u01a1n)","title_en":"The LNSK venue of President HCM, the Central Party, and the Government has met and worked at Phu Xa Pagoda (Vien Son).","description":"","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753435940.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753435226163.jpg","total_access":"11"},{"id":"351","lat":"21.1523036","lon":"105.5060473","district_id":"30","code":"efe937780e95574250dabe07151bdc23","author":"linhttd","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh th\u0103m b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n \u0111a khoa S\u01a1n T\u00e2y (L\u00ea L\u1ee3i)","title_en":"The memorial site of President Ho Chi Minh's visit to Son Tay General Hospital (Le Loi)","description":"","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753439010.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753437257356.jpg","total_access":"10"},{"id":"352","lat":"21.14094885253607","lon":"105.50625764625573","district_id":"30","code":"371bce7dc83817b7893bcdeed13799b5","author":"linhttd","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u01b0u ni\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh th\u0103m tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf U\u1ef7 ban h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh S\u01a1n T\u00e2y (L\u00ea L\u1ee3i)","title_en":"Memorial site of the event of President Ho Chi Minh visiting the headquarters of the Son Tay Administrative Committee (Le Loi)","description":"Tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf \u1ee6y ban h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh t\u1ec9nh S\u01a1n T\u00e2y (nay l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf UBND th\u1ecb x\u00e3 S\u01a1n T\u00e2y) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 vinh d\u1ef1 ba l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u1ec1 th\u0103m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u00e1n b\u1ed9, nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n t\u1ec9nh S\u01a1n T\u00e2y v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 26\/5\/1946, 23\/2\/1958 v\u00e0 8\/7\/1958.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753672490.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753671737864.jpg","total_access":"12"},{"id":"353","lat":"21.130345526856235","lon":"105.50917067499583","district_id":"30","code":"138bb0696595b338afbab333c555292a","author":"linhttd","title":"\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed - Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00f5 b\u1ecb Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n (Nay l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng S\u1ef9 quan L\u1ee5c qu\u00e2n I) (C\u1ed5 \u0110\u00f4ng)","title_en":"Historical site - Tran Quoc Tuan Military Academy (Now is the Army Officer School I) (Co Dong)","description":"N\u1eb1m tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n x\u00e3 C\u1ed5 \u0110\u00f4ng, th\u1ecb x\u00e3 S\u01a1n T\u00e2y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng S\u0129 quan L\u1ee5c qu\u00e2n 1 (t\u00ean ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n) l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o s\u0129 quan ch\u1ec9 huy l\u1ee5c qu\u00e2n c\u1ea5p ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u1ea3i qua 80 n\u0103m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh (15\/4\/1945 \u2013 15\/4\/2025), nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung t\u00e2m gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c \u2013 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u khoa h\u1ecdc qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 T\u1ed5 qu\u1ed1c.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753677296.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753674787218.jpg","total_access":"10"},{"id":"354","lat":"21.13882740792255","lon":"105.50426217129646","district_id":"30","code":"8dd48d6a2e2cad213179a3992c0be53c","author":"linhttd","title":"Th\u00e0nh S\u01a1n T\u00e2y","title_en":"Son Tay Citadel","description":"Th\u00e0nh c\u1ed5 S\u01a1n T\u00e2y n\u1eb1m gi\u1eefa trung t\u00e2m th\u1ecb x\u00e3 S\u01a1n T\u00e2y, c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u01a1n 40km v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda T\u00e2y, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec1u Nguy\u1ec5n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1822 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi vua Minh M\u1ea1ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00f2a th\u00e0nh duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1 ong \u2013 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a v\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t S\u01a1n T\u00e2y \u2013 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3.","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753688359.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753684769798.jpg","total_access":"23"},{"id":"355","lat":"21.069483499996227","lon":"105.49789012294625","district_id":"30","code":"82cec96096d4281b7c95cd7e74623496","author":"linhttd","title":"Ch\u00f9a M\u0103ng (x\u00e3 S\u01a1n \u0110\u00f4ng)","title_en":"Mang Pagoda (Son Dong Commune)","description":"","image":"..\/viewer\/content\/background_1753753826.webp","panorama_image":"pano_1753697041818.jpg","total_access":"12"},{"id":"359","lat":"20.710920715755595","lon":"105.7818923713925","district_id":"28","code":"c058f544c737782deacefa532d9add4c","author":"linhttd","title":"C\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee5 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n L\u1